# BFL Training Project

This is a full-stack web application built with Angular for the frontend (`ShopApp`) and Node.js/Express for the backend (`server`). It demonstrates a basic e-commerce or training platform setup.

## 📁 Project Structure

project/
├── ShopApp/ # Angular 
└── server/ # Node.js backend

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/RishiMk/BFL-Training-Project.git
cd BFL-Training-Project

To Open in VS Code
run in turminal : code .


#In both folders, run:
cd server
npm install

cd ../ShopApp
npm install

#Start the backend server
bash
cd server
node server.js

#Start the Angular frontend
bash
cd ../ShopApp
ng serve


#🌐 View the App
#Once both servers are running, open your browser and go to:
Code
http://localhost:4200
